extensionDescription.message: Supercharge your browser's New Tab with Org-Agenda

matchQuery.description: Name of match query input sent to Emacs

matchQueryTooltip.message:
Default task search string sent to Emacs. This will be used to find a task when no other task is clocked in.

See Org Manual: Matching tags and properties for more information.

Example:
TODO="NEXT"+PRIORITY="A"-@down-@play-@end

wsPort.description: Name of websocket port input to connect to Emacs

wsPortTooltip.message:
WebSocket port to communicate with Emacs. This must match the port specified in your Emacs configuration:

(setq org-newtab-ws-port 35942)
